Cloud Cost Warning
------------------

This platform provisions billable cloud resources. Users are solely responsible
for:
  - Monitoring cloud costs
  - Running cleanup scripts to stop charges
  - Understanding OCI pricing before deployment
  - Setting budget alerts and limits

Estimated costs provided in documentation are approximations only. Actual costs
may vary based on region, usage patterns, and OCI pricing changes.

Security and Compliance
------------------------

Users are responsible for:
